The paper deals with top-$k$ queries on uncertain data, which is a topic related to databases (cs.DB) and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also proposes a ranking function that approximates various top-$k$ definitions, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper evaluates the practical efficiency of the proposed structure, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG).
